<plot>A fourteen year old bed wetter runs home from school every day to retrieve the wet sheet his mother has hung from his bedroom window to punish him. He races to get there before any of his friends pass the house. This enforced training prepares him to become a competitive runner. The script, by 'Michael Landon' (qv), is autobiographical</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572011</url></doc>
